name: eric hutson
text: Horrendous service.  Clerk hung up twice during order, rude, handled other customers during the call with no explanation; & would not answer phone several times when we've tried to order Godfathers @ the Eagle Stop in Lebanon.  Sad, because the pizza was very good previously.

text: I love their pizza it's pretty good.
